{"title":"纤夫谣","authors":["张响钟"],"dates":[{"year":1965,"month":11,"day":28}],"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"纤夫谣"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"张响钟"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一人起歌嘿万人和，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一声声号子嘿雷满山；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"踏平悬崖踩死草嘿，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"百尺桅杆都拉弯！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"潮水冲山嘿山打颤，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"头不发昏嘿步不乱；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"无产阶级骨头硬嘿，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"滔滔逆流拉得转！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"头顶烈日嘿齐拉纤，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"河上还有河嘿山外更有山。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"扛着重担朝前走嘿，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"万里风浪炼好汉！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"云里藏风暴嘿征途伏险关，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"目标正前方嘿那怕千万难；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"顶风顶水跟党走嘿，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"革命的纤绳永不断！"}],"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":6,"page_end":6}